name: Braziliana
description: Braziliana tribal is inspired by ethnic and geometric motifs of indigenous tribes inhabiting Brazilian territory before Portuguese colonization.  The image posted here is a 3D simulation of the art in a frame (the floor and wall are also 3D render).  After purchasing you'll get the high resolution digital file (.ai) It is also a unit from a repeat, this means it can be placed sideways in all directions repeatedly, creating an infinite pattern.
